import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from 'docz'
import { Checkbox } from '../src'

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"checkbox"}}>{`Checkbox`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"default"}}>{`Default`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={0} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Checkbox>Default</Checkbox>`} __scope={{props,Checkbox}}>
  <Checkbox>Default</Checkbox>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"hover"}}>{`Hover`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={1} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Checkbox hover>Default</Checkbox>`} __scope={{props,Checkbox}}>
  <Checkbox hover>Default</Checkbox>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"selected"}}>{`Selected`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={2} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Checkbox selected>Click me</Checkbox>`} __scope={{props,Checkbox}}>
  <Checkbox selected>Click me</Checkbox>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"disabled"}}>{`Disabled`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={3} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Checkbox disabled>Click me</Checkbox>`} __scope={{props,Checkbox}}>
  <Checkbox disabled>Click me</Checkbox>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"selected-and-disabled"}}>{`Selected and disabled`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={4} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Checkbox selected disabled>
  Click me
</Checkbox>`} __scope={{props,Checkbox}}>
  <Checkbox selected disabled>
    Click me
  </Checkbox>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"error"}}>{`Error`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={5} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Checkbox error>Click me</Checkbox>`} __scope={{props,Checkbox}}>
  <Checkbox error>Click me</Checkbox>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"error-with-hover"}}>{`Error with hover`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={6} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Checkbox error hover>
  Click me
</Checkbox>`} __scope={{props,Checkbox}}>
  <Checkbox error hover>
    Click me
  </Checkbox>
</Playground>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"error-and-selected"}}>{`Error and selected`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={7} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Checkbox error selected>
  Click me
</Checkbox>`} __scope={{props,Checkbox}}>
  <Checkbox error selected>
    Click me
  </Checkbox>
</Playground></MDXTag>
